'''尼祖·李奧曲加'''（{{lang-en|'''Nigel Reo-Coker'''}}，{{bd|1984年|5月14日|catIdx=Reo-Coker, Nigel}}）是[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[職業|職業]]職業足球員，司職[[中場|中場]]。為球迷熟悉的是擁有準確攔截及高素質傳球能力。李奧曲加在[[溫布頓足球會|溫布頓]]開始足球運動員生涯，2004年改投[[韋斯咸|韋斯咸]]，在2007年加盟[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]，最後效力[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[米爾頓凱恩斯足球會|米尔顿凯恩斯]]。

==生平==
=== 早年 ===
尼祖·李奧曲加在1984年5月14日生於[[倫敦|倫敦]][[克羅伊登|克羅伊登]]（Croydon）<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.englandfootballonline.com/TeamPlyrsBios/PlayersR/BioReoCokerNSA.html |title=Nigel Reo-Coker Profile |publisher=England Football Online |accessdate=2009-11-10 |archive-date=2008-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080829105113/http://www.englandfootballonline.com/TeamPlyrsBios/PlayersR/BioReoCokerNSA.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在兒童時期曾在[[塞拉里昂|塞拉里昂]]居住長達6年，當時他的父親在當地任職[[醫生|醫生]]。1990年父母離婚後，他與兩名妹妹跟隨母親返回倫敦居住<ref name="Times">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/article714135.ece?token=null&offset=12 |title=The Big Interview: Nigel Reo Coker |publisher=Times Online |date=7 May 2006 |accessdate=3 June 2007}}</ref>。

=== 球會 ===
;溫布頓
李奧曲加於12歲時代表[[克羅伊登區|克羅伊登區]]作賽時被[[倫敦|倫敦]]球會[[溫布頓足球會|溫布頓]]發掘到<ref name="Indie">{{cite news|language=en |url=http://sport.independent.co.uk/football/premiership/article344718.ece |title=Nigel Reo-Coker: 'It annoys me when... |date=2006-02-11 |publisher=The Independent on Sunday |accessdate=2007-06-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927194407/http://sport.independent.co.uk/football/premiership/article344718.ece |archivedate=2007-09-27 }}</ref>，他在球隊的青訓系統成長，被提升上一隊後更獲委任為[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]<ref name="Indie2">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qn4159/is_20040118/ai_n9691154 |title=Hot property Reo-Coker has to sweat it out |date=2004-01-18 |publisher=The Independent on Sunday |accessdate=2007-06-03 |archive-date=2007-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071231003005/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qn4159/is_20040118/ai_n9691154 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其間已經獲選為[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]代表首次上陣<ref name="U21">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wimbledon/3172670.stm |title=Reo-Coker hopes to impress |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=7 October 2003 |accessdate=3 June 2007 |archive-date=2003-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031010202628/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wimbledon/3172670.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2003年[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]領隊[[哈里·雷德克纳普|哈里·雷德克纳普]]已承諾收購李奧曲加，將他帶到這支準備首次升班到[[英超|英超]]作賽的南部海岸球隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/2995190.stm |title=Pompey agree Reo-Coker fee |date=2003-06-16 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2007-06-03 |archive-date=2003-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031221221104/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/2995190.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但球隊因財困導致李奧曲加雖然已簽約樸茨茅夫而仍然留效溫布頓<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/3135805.stm |title=Pompey concede Dons duo defeat |date=2003-08-08 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2007-06-03 |archive-date=2003-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030809021956/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/3135805.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，李奧曲加為溫布頓合共上陣64場及射入6球<ref name=sbase>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=30923 |title=Nigel Reo-Coker |work=Soccerbase |accessdate=2007-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070804070105/http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=30923 |archive-date=2007-08-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

;韋斯咸
2003/04年上半季李奧曲加表現出色，他於2004年1月獲[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]賞識收歸旗下<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/3414953.stm |title=Reo-Coker signs for Hammers |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=22 January 2004 |accessdate=3 June 2007 |archive-date=2004-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040202213800/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/3414953.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他迅即成為[[Alan_Pardew|阿倫·柏祖]]（Alan Pardew）一隊的常規正選及擔任[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]。2004/05年首個[[英冠|英冠]]球季李奧曲加射入3球協助球隊取得聯賽第6位及參加升班附加賽資格，韋斯咸先後擊敗[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]及[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]透過附加賽升班[[英超|英超]]。更於2006年帶領韋斯咸晉級[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]決賽，對手為6屆冠軍[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]，韋斯咸於完場前領先3-2，但在補時被[[史提芬·謝拉特|謝拉特]]射入「世界波」扳平，[[加時賽|加時]]雙方再無紀錄，韋斯咸於[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]1-3敗陣屈居亞軍<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.fa-cupfinals.co.uk/2006.htm |title=Liverpool 3 West Ham 3 (Liverpool win 3-1 on Penalties) |publisher=fa-cupfinals.co.uk |date= |accessdate=2009-11-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090421125912/http://www.fa-cupfinals.co.uk/2006.htm |archivedate=2009-04-21 }}</ref>。

[[2006年至2007年英格蘭超級聯賽|2006/07年球季]]韋斯咸開季成績差勁，李奧曲加成為代罪羔羊<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/6192317.stm |title=Reo-Coker subjected to hate mail |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=19 December 2007 |accessdate=5 June 2007 |archive-date=2007-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070128135239/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/6192317.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/6238689.stm |title=West Ham boss defends Reo-Coker |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=7 January 2007 |accessdate=5 June 2007 |archive-date=2007-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070910171213/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/6238689.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，球隊排名接近降班區域，最終導致領隊阿倫·柏祖被辭退<small><ref>{{cite news|language=en |url=http://sport.independent.co.uk/football/premiership/article2201053.ece |title=West Ham 'need a bit of luck', says Reo-Coker |publisher=Independent Online |date=31 January 2007 |accessdate=3 June 2007 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070331091722/http://sport.independent.co.uk/football/premiership/article2201053.ece |archivedate=2007-03-31}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/6174627.stm |title=Reo-Coker reveals West Ham doubts |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=13 December 2006 |accessdate=3 June 2007}}</ref></small>。李奧曲加在球季末回復狀態，協助韋斯咸在最後9輪聯賽勝出7場，在聯賽煞科日作客當屆聯賽冠軍[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]1-0獲勝，確定逃出降班漩渦<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/6652329.stm |title=Magnusson hails West Ham survival |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=14 May 2007 |accessdate=5 June 2007 |archive-date=2009-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090220024033/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_ham_utd/6652329.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。李奧曲加在未能獲得韋斯咸董事會保證其在球隊的未來後提出轉會要求<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/standard-sport/article-23398136-reo-coker-asks-for-transfer.do |title=Reo-Coker asks for transfer |publisher=thisislondon.co.uk |date=2007-05-27 |accessdate=2009-11-10 }}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，據報[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]在6月提出700萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]希望羅致他<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/6724387.stm |title=Aston Villa bid £7m for Reo-Coker |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=5 June 2007 |accessdate=5 June 2007 |archive-date=2007-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070828220525/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/6724387.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終韋斯咸與阿士東維拉在7月達成協議，以約850萬英鎊將其隊長出售到維拉<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.avfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/News/HeadlinesDetail/0,,10265~1067819,00.html |title=Reo-Coker Fee Agreed |publisher=阿士東維拉官網 |date=4 July 2007 |accessdate=4 July 2007 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070707010116/http://www.avfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/News/HeadlinesDetail/0,,10265~1067819,00.html |archivedate=2007年7月7日 }}</ref>。

;阿士東維拉
李奧曲加於2007年7月5日以據報850萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]轉投[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]，簽約四年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/6260924.stm |title=Villa complete Reo-Coker signing |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=5 July 2007 |accessdate=5 July 20077}}</ref>，他在8月28日[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第二圈5-0擊敗[[雷克斯汉姆足球俱乐部|域斯咸]]射入轉會後首個入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/6963522.stm |title=Wrexham 0-5 Aston Villa |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=28 August 2007 |accessdate=3 September 2009 |archive-date=2008-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080720085341/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/6963522.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。李奧曲加居於[[斯托桥|斯托桥]]（Stourbridge），接近隊友[[艾殊利·楊格|艾殊利·楊格]]的居所。2008年1月21日在常任[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]][[加雷斯·巴里|巴里]]因傷缺陣，李奧曲加戴上隊長臂章在[[晏菲路球場|晏菲路球場]]出戰[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]。他在作客[[白鹿徑球場|白鹿徑球場]]對陣[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]時射入首個加盟維拉後的[[英超|英超]]入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7601910.stm |title=Tottenham 1-2 Aston Villa |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=15 September 2008 |accessdate=15 September 2008 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304203851/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7601910.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；在三日後[[歐洲足協盃|歐洲足協盃]]對[[保加利亞|保加利亞]]的[[利特克斯足球俱乐部|列迪斯洛維治]]李奧曲加再取得入球，為球隊扳平1-1，最終維拉以3-1奏凱而回<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7615244.stm |title=Litex Lovech 1-3 Aston Villa |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=18 September 2008 |accessdate=2 September 2009 |archive-date=2008-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080921220332/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7615244.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。期間李奧曲加主要擔任[[後衛_(足球)|右閘]]，當右翼球員缺陣時亦會推前擔任[[中場|翼鋒]]。

在2009年[[和平盃足球賽|和平盃]]的後段比賽，因原任隊長[[斯蒂利揚·彼得羅夫|-{zh-hans:彼得罗夫;zh-hk:柏度夫;zh-tw:彼得羅夫;}-]]受傷，李奧曲加代任隊長，直到決賽憑[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]4-3擊敗[[尤文图斯足球俱乐部|祖雲達斯]]後，李奧曲加以隊長身份高舉獎盃<ref>{{cite news|language=en |url=http://www.birminghammail.net/birmingham-sport/aston-villa-fc/aston-villa-news/2009/08/03/aston-villa-4-juventus-3-97319-24302013/ |title=Aston Villa 4 Juventus 3 - Bill Howell's pre-season verdict |publisher=birminghammail.net |date=2009-08-03 |accessdate=2009-11-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110917054003/http://www.birminghammail.net/birmingham-sport/aston-villa-fc/aston-villa-news/2009/08/03/aston-villa-4-juventus-3-97319-24302013/ |archivedate=2011-09-17 }}</ref>。在[[加雷斯·巴里|巴里]]離隊轉投[[曼城足球俱乐部|曼城]]後，李奧曲加原本可以再次取回正選席位，擔任擅長的[[中場|防守中場]]之職，但在2009年9月18日在訓練場上與領隊[[馬田·奧尼爾|馬田·奧尼爾]]發生爭執，更自此一直被「雪藏」而沒有上陣機會<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/8263129.stm |title=Reo-Coker dropped and sent home |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-09-18 |accessdate=2009-11-10}}</ref>。直到11月7日才獲「解凍」，以[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]身份於主場5-1擊敗[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]再次獲派上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8344717.stm |title=Aston Villa 5-1 Bolton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-11-07 |accessdate=2009-11-10 |archive-date=2009-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091109054433/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8344717.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，馬田·奧尼爾更稱兩人雖然曾有誤會，但在柏度夫受傷時，他絕無猶豫將隊長臂章給予李奧曲加<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/8350537.stm |title=Reo-Coker row forgotten - O'Neill |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-11-09 |accessdate=2009-11-10 |archive-date=2009-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091111220303/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/a/aston_villa/8350537.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年5月27日於球季結束後，李奧曲加成為10名遭維拉放棄的球員之一<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13572464.stm |title=Nigel Reo-Coker and John Carew leave Aston Villa |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-27 |accessdate=2011-07-28 |archive-date=2011-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811233730/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13572464.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

